Package jsongminer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConfigDataAndParser
    Objects of this class hold basic configuration settings that are accessible via their public fields.
    DublinCoreInterpreter
    This is s utility class containing static methods for processing collections of MusicMetaData objects into Dublin Core-formatted collections of MusicMetaData.
    EchoNestMiner
    Objects of this class are used to identify songs and extract information about them from the Echo Nest API.
    EmbeddedTagMiner
    An object of this class is used to extract embedded metadata from an audio file.
    LastFMMiner
    Objects of this class are used to extract information from the Last.FM API with respect to a given song.
    Main
    jSongMiner is a system for identifying music using fingerprinting of audio and/or the use of embedded metadata.
    MainMethods
    This class holds static methods that are called by the Main method of the Main class.
    MusicBrainzMiner
    Objects of this class are used to extract information from the Music Brainz API with respect to a given song.
    MusicMetaData
    Each object of this class holds a piece of metadata, including the field identifer for the metadata, the value itself of the metadata and the source from which the metadata value was derived.
